# outputs

**Instance Property**

An array of outputs associated with the player item.

## Declaration

```swift
nonisolated var outputs: [AVPlayerItemOutput] { get }
```

## Discussion

This property contains the collection of [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVPlayerItemOutput] objects used to transfer media data to the player object.

## Managing player item outputs

- **add(_:)**: Adds the specified player item output object to the receiver.
- **remove(_:)**: Removes the specified player item output object from the receiver.
